<p align="center">
NahIdWin is <strong>NOT</strong> a community-driven pastel theme that aims to <strong>ACTUALLY</strong> be the middle ground between low and high-contrast themes, absolutely perfect for <strong>VIBE CODING</strong>. Written in Vanilla JSON. This theme is unfortunately not powered by AI.

</p>

### 👐 Contributing

You can contribute by starring this repo and putting the fries in the bag little bro 🥀

### 🗣️ Supported Languages

Only Python and JSON are supported for now. Feel free to submit a PR or change your code to one of the supported languages — it will be easier to switch languages than to find a color theme as good as this one fr.
